data.description: Welcome home to this incredibly charming 3-bed, 2-bath brick ranch in Berkeley!  This home offers a bright living room with hardwood flooring; an eat-in kitchen with loads of storage, new countertops and new stainless appliances; spacious bedrooms; a detached 2-car garage and finished basement!  Just unpack and enjoy!  This is a must see.  Schedule a showing today.
